## Pre-commit Hook Enforcement

### Backend Check

```bash
# In .husky/pre-commit
echo "▶️  Compiling with zero warnings enforcement..."
mvn compile -q
if [ $? -ne 0 ]; then
  echo "❌ Compilation failed or warnings detected"
  echo "   Java compiler warnings are NOT allowed"
  exit 1
fi
```

**Runs:** Every commit with backend changes  
**Time:** 10-20 seconds  
**Blocks commit:** Yes, if warnings found

### Frontend Check

```bash
# In .husky/pre-commit (via lint-staged)
npx lint-staged

# lint-staged config:
"*.{ts,tsx}": [
  "eslint --fix --max-warnings 0"  # Zero warnings enforced
]
```

**Runs:** Every commit with frontend changes  
**Time:** 5-10 seconds  
**Blocks commit:** Yes, if warnings found

